summary: This mods adds a trap door under the ladder in Breezehome, located in Whiterun that takes you to the test room.
descriptionHtml:
Has not conflicted with any mods I have. I was surprised there wasn\'t a mod like this already here. I searched but couldn\'t find one. I mainly like how all the crafting stuff is all grouped together. I added a few more lights but if it\'s still to dark for some of you just say so and I\'ll add a few more.

Just download/unzip and put TestAreaTeleport.esp in your Skyrim data folder. Use the Nexus Client to activate it.

4-45-12
-Added access to/from all player homes.
-Added a chest with plenty of crafting supplies. *NOTE I couldn\'t find small/large animal pelts in the list. You can easily obtain some of those from the skinning rack.
-I tried to improve the lighting but now blocky type shadows appear. I\'m still trying to figure that out.....

Next update will add a chest for ones alchemy needs.

To uninstall the mod simply delete TestAreaTeleport.esp
author: vince--
